name: Rystall
Lore: 'Musician. Raised by Ortolans. Grew up on the streets of Coruscant. Rescued from the Black Sun crime cartel by Lando Calrissian.',
Text: 'Power and forfeit +2 at a Coruscant site. May retrieve 1 Force each time your deploy a musician to same site. Once during each of your turns, may use 1 Force to ''charm'' one male of ability < 3 present- male is forfeit = 0 for remainder of turn.',
